snippet.title: Autobahn Police Simulator 2 - Highway Accident! Gameplay 4K
snippet.description:
Autobahn Police Simulator 2018 - Highway Accident Gameplay 4K video.

Start your even more exciting career as law enforcer on Europe’s fastest road now with the successor to the popular Autobahn Police Simulator.

For the first time in Autobahn Police Simulator 2 you can use the Character Creator to customize your own in-game character’s head, body and even clothing to your liking.

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/483770/Autobahn_Police_Simulator_2/

Minimum system requirements:
- OS: Windows 7 / 8 / 10.
- CPU: Quad Core with 3 GHz (64bit).
- Memory: 4 GB RAM.
- Graphics: GPU with 1 GB VRAM, e.g. Nvidia GeForce GTX 760 or similar (Onboard chips are not officially supported).

My Config: Intel core i7, 16GB RAM, GTX 1070.

Feel free to ask any questions you have!
